headline: CF Industries (NYSE:CF) Launches Carbon Capture Unit, Eyes Growth in Low-Carbon Ammonia Market
summary: CF Industries (NYSE:CF) is one of the best commodity stocks to buy. On July 14, 2025, the company marked a major step in its low-carbon transition by launching a new CO₂ dehydration and compression unit at its Donaldsonville Complex.
